    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a well-sorted 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S (996.2). This example features the 3.6L M96 horizontally opposed six-cylinder powerplant paired with a precise 6-speed G96 longitudinal manual transaxle. The wide-body chassis houses a viscous-clutch all-wheel-drive system, providing superior mechanical grip and high-speed stability. Recent preventative maintenance includes a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal to address common M96 failure points. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for neutral cornering dynamics. This C4S exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage but remains a mechanically sound driver\u2019s machine with a linear power band and exceptional deceleration provided by four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
