      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car! It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape. It's super reliable, runs smoothly, and is totally ready for its next adventure. I've truly loved driving this beauty, but it's time for someone else to get behind the wheel. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
